        "created_at": "2025-06-09T14:28:34.986Z",
        "cooked": "<p>How do you dismiss the notification? On my device, this will not swipe away.</p>\n<p>If that notification is disables, it can’t be dismissed anyway.</p>\n<p>I do agree that there should be a way to manually lock Signal from within the client. A home screen or lock screen widget would work too.</p>",
