        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"CueHD\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"69633\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/cuehd/48/42510_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> CueHD:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>How do you dismiss the notification? On my device, this will not swipe away.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>I’m not sure what version it changed in, but newer Android versions don’t allow persistent notifications. Everything can be dismissed.</p>",
